OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776957067
OL,3,CMemorial unveiled to honour PC Andrew
OL,4,CHarper who died in the line of duty
OL,6,FA memorial has been unveiled in
OL,7,FReading in honour of a Thames Valley
OL,8,Fpolice officer who died in the line of
OL,9,Fduty.
OL,11,FPc Andrew Harper had been married just
OL,12,Fa month, and was due to go on
OL,13,Fhoneymoon when he was killed while
OL,14,Fresponding to a burglary in
OL,15,FSulhamstead on 15 August 2019.
OL,17,FOn Thursday (23 April) local MPs,
OL,18,Fcivic dignitaries and representatives
OL,19,Fof national police associations joined
OL,20,FPc Harper's family and friends to
OL,21,Fremember the sacrifice he made.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
