PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776957067
OL,3,CMemorial unveiled to honour PC Andrew
OL,4,CHarper who died in the line of duty
OL,6,FThe stone memorial is the 61st
OL,7,Fmemorial to fallen police officers
OL,8,Fthat the Police Memorial Trust has
OL,9,Ferected.
OL,11,FThe independent charity was founded by
OL,12,Fthe late film producer Michael Winner.
OL,14,FFollowing his death, his widow Lissie
OL,15,FHarper campaigned, and successfully
OL,16,Fimplemented Harper's Law.
OL,18,FIt gives extended mandatory life
OL,19,Fsentences to anyone who commits the
OL,20,Fmanslaughter of an emergency worker on
OL,21,Fduty.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776957067
OL,3,CMemorial unveiled to honour PC Andrew
OL,4,CHarper who died in the line of duty
OL,6,FLissie gave a moving tribute at the
OL,7,Fceremony in Reading. "Today we gather
OL,8,Fto remember and honour my late husband
OL,9,FAndrew," she began.
OL,11,F"A man who meant so much to so many,
OL,12,Fand everything to me.
OL,14,F"He was proud to serve as a police
OL,15,Fofficer, but to me he was so much
OL,16,Fmore. He was my partner, my strength
OL,17,Fand my first love.
OL,19,F"He had a kind heart, a steady
OL,20,Fpresence, and a quiet courage that
OL,21,Fshaped the way he lived every day.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776957067
OL,3,CMemorial unveiled to honour PC Andrew
OL,4,CHarper who died in the line of duty
OL,6,F"In August 2019 our lives changed
OL,7,Fforever.
OL,9,F"The world lost a hero, but I lost the
OL,10,Fperson I was meant to grow old with -
OL,11,Fthe man I stood beside on our wedding
OL,12,Fday, promising a lifetime we never got
OL,13,Fto finish.
OL,15,F"There are no words for that kind of
OL,16,Floss, but there is love - a love that
OL,17,Fhasn't faded, and never will. I will
OL,18,Falways carry him with me, in my heart,
OL,19,Fin my memories, and in everything he
OL,20,Ftaught me about strength, compassion
OL,21,Fand courage.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776957067
OL,3,CMemorial unveiled to honour PC Andrew
OL,4,CHarper who died in the line of duty
OL,6,F"Andrew never took life for granted.
OL,7,FHe gave his all in every aspect of his
OL,8,Flife, always finding value in the
OL,9,Feveryday.
OL,11,F"He was the epitome of what a police
OL,12,Fofficer should be, willing to protect
OL,13,Fand serve at all costs.
OL,15,F"That is why I know how important it
OL,16,Fis that Andrew is honoured with this
OL,17,Fmemorial, and I am so grateful to the
OL,18,FTrust and everyone involved in making
OL,19,Fit happen.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776957067
OL,3,CMemorial unveiled to honour PC Andrew
OL,4,CHarper who died in the line of duty
OL,6,F"I hope that those who walk these
OL,7,Fstreets will take a moment to pause,
OL,8,Fto pay their respects, and to know
OL,9,Fthat he made our world a safer place.
OL,11,F"He deserved so much more, but we will
OL,12,Fcherish all that he gave.
OL,14,F"Andrew, you are missed, you are
OL,15,Floved, and you will never be
OL,16,Fforgotten."
OL,18,FPc Harper was responding to a report
OL,19,Fof a burglary and the theft of a quad
OL,20,Fbike on 15 August 2019.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
