PN,41307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776957067
OL,3,CMemorial unveiled to honour PC Andrew
OL,4,CHarper who died in the line of duty
OL,6,FAs he tried to stop the group, he
OL,7,Fbecame caught in a tow rope and was
OL,8,Fdragged for a mile along a country
OL,9,Flane - he was pronounced dead at the
OL,10,Fscene.
OL,12,FHenry Long, 19, was in the driving
OL,13,Fseat with passengers' 17-year-olds
OL,14,FAlbert Bowers and Jessie Cole.
OL,16,FLong was jailed for 16 years and both
OL,17,FBowers and Cole were sentenced to 13
OL,18,Fyears in prison.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776957067
OL,3,CMemorial unveiled to honour PC Andrew
OL,4,CHarper who died in the line of duty
OL,6,FSpeaking after the ceremony Detective
OL,7,FSergeant Edward Crofts said: "I think
OL,8,Fit's been a number of years since his
OL,9,Ftragic death, and I think this point
OL,10,Fin time is ideal as a mark of respect
OL,11,Fand to thank him for all his work as a
OL,12,Fpolice officer.
OL,14,F"To thank him for the ultimate
OL,15,Fsacrifice that he made."
OL,17,FSpeaking about Pc Harper he added: "He
OL,18,Fwas, as a police officer, the exact
OL,19,Fsort of police officer you would want.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
