PN,41309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776957067
OL,3,CMemorial unveiled to honour PC Andrew
OL,4,CHarper who died in the line of duty
OL,6,F"Very dedicated, very driven, he was
OL,7,Ffunny, he was very well liked with
OL,8,Fcolleagues, he was a great guy."
OL,10,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,11,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,12,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,13,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,14,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,15,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/9
